data.description:
This house has everything a large family has been searching for! Outstanding location on Quiet Street, Fenced yard for kids and pets!
Close to Big Surf and Hwy 54 for easy access! Large private deck. Modern Metal Roofing. Easy level entrance. Main Level living with a Huge Master Suite that offers a sitting area and or attached office. Kitchen with an attached dining room. 2 more bedrooms on main level for kiddos. Large lower living area with large bedroom and a huge master suite including jacuzzi bath. Walkout basement.  Full Bath with wash tub / utility room on lower level. This house is a must see for the money!!! Amazing deal for the price per square footage!  $20,000 Price Reduction to $259,900.
